eNCA's Morena Mothupi speaks to Drickus Botha from the Transvaal Agricultural Union SA. Courtesy #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - Agricultural organisation TLU SA is urging Eskom to address its challenges, rather than punishing everyone. Drickus Botha from TLU SA says the utility must issue load reduction notices as the power outages have a severe impact on the sector. Farmers are getting frustrated with Eskom’s load reduction policy saying its collective punishment.